# Not build inputs. These change often (docs, CI and browser-test commits), and
# anything left here invalidates the `COPY . .` layer and with it the whole
# wasm+cargo build. Root *.md stays: several are read at build time (README as
# the workspace `readme`, CHANGELOG by the webapp version script's fallbacks).
#
# This is the only ignore file either image gets. Both builds use the repo root
# as context, and BuildKit reads `<context>/.dockerignore` or a sibling
# `<dockerfile>.dockerignore` - never a `.dockerignore` that merely lives beside
# the image's other sources.
